  "name": "Elmina",
  "title": "Yuletide Rogue",
  "description": "\"Hey! Watch where you're going, you nearly made me drop my stuff!\"\n\n\"What are you rushing around for, anyway? All the good stuff in this market's already been snatched up. Don't tell me you're one of those people who put their shopping off to the last minute.\"\n\n\"...sigh. Of course you are. I should have guessed.\"\n\n\"Well, don't just stand there. Follow me. I know a couple places that can help you out, but you better not do this again, you hear? The people in your life must really care about you. What's the point of Christmas if you don't give them something special?\"",
